      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5855 - Abdullah ibn Abbas narrated from the Messenger of Allah (swt), peace and blessings be upon him and his family, that the Prophet (sw) said:\n\"The nobles of my nation are the bearers of the Qur'an and those who engage in prayer during the night.\""
